Hello! Thank you for calling Harmony Music School. My name is Gary Hill. Could I have your name, please?

Hi, Gary. My name is Sandra Morgan. I'm feeling a bit nervous about my request today.

No worries at all, Sandra. I'm here to help you. How can I assist you today?

I'd like to inquire about returning a music book I purchased last week.

I understand. Could you please provide me with your order number?

Yes, the order number is one two three four five.

Thank you, Sandra. I can confirm that order. Could I also have the last four digits of the card you used for the purchase?

It's eight nine seven six.

Great, all set. We've received your return request, and it will be processed in the next three to five business days.

Thank you so much, Gary. I appreciate your help.

You're welcome, Sandra. Thank you for your time, and I hope you have a wonderful day!
